sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant IndividualProvidedDetailsController
    participant HMRC_Auth as HMRC Auth
    participant MongoDB as MongoDB (individual)

    Client->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: PUT /individual-provided-details/for-individual (IndividualProvidedDetails JSON)
    IndividualProvidedDetailsController->>HMRC_Auth: Authenticate (GG, Individual affinity)
    alt Auth fails
        HMRC_Auth-->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: 401 Unauthorised
        IndividualProvidedDetailsController-->>Client: 401 Unauthorised
    else Auth succeeds
        HMRC_Auth-->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: Authenticated
        IndividualProvidedDetailsController->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: Parse request body
        alt Body parse fails
            IndividualProvidedDetailsController-->>Client: 400 Bad Request
        else Body parse succeeds
            Note over IndividualProvidedDetailsController: ensureInternalUserId exists but is NOT called
            IndividualProvidedDetailsController->>MongoDB: upsert (filter: internalUserId + agentApplicationId)
            MongoDB-->>IndividualProvidedDetailsController: Updated/Inserted
            IndividualProvidedDetailsController-->>Client: 200 OK (IndividualProvidedDetails JSON)
        end
    end
